        {
            "title": "世界杯影響 澳門六月賭收按月跌近兩成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fmXCoNqThV75566juHA00w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/the_bamboo_works_186/ab7c88598547eece33479e51bfeb3a3d\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
